===Noun phrase===
'''[[prepositional]] [[phrase]]'''
#{{grammar}} a phrase that has both a preposition and its [[object]]; may be used as an [[adjective]] or an [[adverb]]
For example:
*''The man '''in the story''' walked '''along the beach'''.''

